d_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4366360581\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/5183#issuecomment-4366360581\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/5183\",\"id\":4366360581,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBEFgBQ\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T14:11:05Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T14:11:05Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `org.eclipse.jdt:ecj:3.34.0`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-5183-fails-native-image-run-org.eclipse.jdt-ecj-3.34.0-0ed92485\\n\\nRun metrics were unavailable, but the logs point to `run-consecutive-tests` timing out after Gradle had already reported success, not to a reproducible `ecj` metadata/native-image failure. `checkMetadataFiles` succeeded in all observed reruns (`logs/check-metadata-files/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-03T13-54-39-794442Z.log`, `logs/check-metadata-files/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-03T13-56-22-347106Z.log`, `logs/check-metadata-files/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-03T13-58-00-730032Z.log`). In `logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-03T13-38-18-694491Z.log`, the native-image test run reports 18/18 tests successful and `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`, then the wrapper is killed by the 5 minute timeout (`TIMEOUT: 'native-image run' ... exit code 137`); the follow-up `javac compile` bisect also shows `BUILD SUCCESSFUL` before another timeout. The same pattern appears in `logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-03T13-58-25-302386Z.log` under `future-defaults-all`. For comparison, `logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-03T13-54-43-671223Z.log` and `logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-03T13-56-24-745122Z.log` both end with `PASSED:3.34.0`, which makes this look flaky and likely related to process shutdown/timeout handling rather than missing reachability metadata.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-03T13-38-18-694491Z.log`\\n- `logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-03T13-58-25-302386Z.log`\\n- `logs/run-consecutive-tests/local-ci/bash-2026-05-03T13-54-43-671223Z.log`\\n- `logs/check-metadata-files/local-ci/gradlew-2026-05-03T13-58-00-730032Z.log`\\n- `logs/org.eclipse.jdt:ecj:3.34.0/local-ci-fixup/run-consecutive-tests-2026-05-03T13-48-58-850663Z.log`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Re-run `run-consecutive-tests.sh` for `org.eclipse.jdt:ecj:3.34.0` in both `current-defaults` and `future-defaults-all` modes and check whether any Gradle/Java process remains alive after `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`.\\n2. Compare the passing runs (`13-54-43`, `13-56-24`) against the timed-out runs (`13-38-18`, `13-58-25`) to isolate the shutdown difference.\\n3. If the timeout reproduces, capture thread/process state at the 5 minute mark and adjust the harness timeout/process handling instead of changing `ecj` reachability metadata.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4366360581/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":25108106891,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABBJO2ws8AAAAF2I9Oiw\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25108106891\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/u